Four members of the same family including two children were burnt to death during a Monday night  fire in Likoni area in Mombasa. The husband of the deceased woman who is suspected to have started the fire following a domestic quarrel was however rescued from the inferno and rushed to the Coast General Hospital where he is receiving treatment pending his appearance in court. In Meru county, a police officer based at Siakago was rushed to the Kenyatta National Hospital after her husband set their house on fire killing himself and their 2 months old baby. 